<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Beamtenhelden – Versicherungsberatung für Beamte</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy:   #030039;
      --blue:   #2200c8;
      --sky:    #51bdff;
      --coral:  #fc5b47;
      --white:  #ffffff;
      --silver: #dcdcdc;
      --light:  #f4f5fa;
      --muted:  #6b7280;
      --font:   'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--white); color: var(--navy); overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .nav-top {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 0.75rem 2.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .nav-logo-wrap {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo-wrap img { height: 70px; width: auto; }
    .nav-cta-wrap {
      position: absolute; right: 2.5rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--coral); color: var(--white);
      padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.88rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .nav-divider {
      height: 1px; background: var(--light);
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--white);
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      padding: 10rem 2.5rem 6rem;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }
    .eyebrow-line { width: 32px; height: 2px; background: var(--coral); }
    .eyebrow-text {
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--coral);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3.5vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.06; color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.15s ease both;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.25s ease both;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--navy); color: var(--white);
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s; display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue); }
    .btn-outline {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--navy); color: var(--navy);
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s; display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue); }

    /* hero right: stats */
    .hero-stats { animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.35s ease both; }
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: #e5e7eb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--white); padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .stat-card:hover { background: var(--light); }
    .stat-num { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .stat-accent { color: var(--coral); }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ── TRUST BAR ── */
    .trustbar {
      background: var(--navy); padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .trust-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 300;
      padding: 0.25rem 1.5rem;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }
    .trust-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .trust-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--coral); flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    .section-light { background: var(--white); padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
    .section-tinted { background: var(--light); padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
    .section-dark { background: var(--navy); padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-eyebrow {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-eyebrow .eyebrow-line { width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--coral); }
    .section-eyebrow .eyebrow-text { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--coral); }
    .section-eyebrow-light .eyebrow-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .section-eyebrow-light .eyebrow-line { background: var(--coral); }
    .section-title { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .section-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue); }
    .section-title-light { color: var(--white); }
    .section-title-light em { color: var(--sky); }
    .section-sub { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); max-width: 560px; }
    .section-sub-light { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
    .section-header { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }

    /* ── LEISTUNGEN ── */
    .leistungen-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .leistung-card {
      padding: 2.25rem 2rem; border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .leistung-card:nth-child(3n) { border-right: none; }
    .leistung-card:nth-last-child(-n+3) { border-bottom: none; }
    .leistung-card:hover { background: var(--light); }
    .leistung-card::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;
      width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--coral);
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }
    .leistung-card:hover::after { width: 100%; }
    .leistung-num {
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--coral); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
    }
    .leistung-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.3; }
    .leistung-text { font-size: 0.86rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── BERATER ── */
    .berater-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .berater-card {
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: var(--white);
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .berater-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(3,0,57,0.1); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .berater-top {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .berater-avatar {
      width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--navy);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--white);
    }
    .berater-name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
    .berater-role {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .berater-bottom { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
    .berater-book {
      display: block; text-align: center;
      background: var(--navy); color: var(--white);
      padding: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.88rem;
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .berater-book:hover { background: var(--blue); }

    /* ── WARUM ── */
    .warum-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .warum-item {
      padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .warum-item:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
    .warum-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .warum-check {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--coral);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .warum-check svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: var(--coral); fill: none; stroke-width: 2.5; }
    .warum-title { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .warum-text { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── PROZESS ── */
    .prozess-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }
    .prozess-step {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem; border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
    }
    .prozess-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .step-num-wrap {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: var(--navy); color: var(--white);
      font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.88rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .step-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #e5e7eb; }
    .step-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .step-text { font-size: 0.86rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      background: var(--blue); padding: 5rem 2.5rem; text-align: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-section::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute;
      top: -100px; right: -100px;
      width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(3,0,57,0.3); pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-section::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute;
      bottom: -80px; left: -80px;
      width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(252,91,71,0.15); pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; position: relative; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; position: relative; }
    .btn-white {
      background: var(--white); color: var(--navy);
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; display: inline-block;
      position: relative;
    }
    .btn-white:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy); padding: 2.5rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .footer-logo img { height: 48px; width: auto; opacity: 0.9; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .footer-links a { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .leistungen-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .leistung-card:nth-child(3n) { border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      .leistung-card:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
      .berater-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .warum-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .warum-item:nth-child(2n) { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
      .prozess-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .prozess-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      .nav-top { padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; }
      .nav-cta-wrap { right: 1.25rem; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      .section-light, .section-tinted, .section-dark { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
      .hero { padding: 9rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
      .trustbar { gap: 0; }
      .trust-item { padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-top">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo-wrap">
      <!-- Logo – wird als Bild eingebettet -->
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Beamtenhelden" />
    </a>
    <div class="nav-cta-wrap">
      <a href="#berater" class="nav-cta">Termin buchen</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Eyebrow-Text Hero -->
        <span class="eyebrow-text">Unabhängige Versicherungsberatung für Beamte</span>
      </div>
      <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Haupt-Überschrift Hero -->
      <h1>Versicherungsschutz,<br>der zu <em>deinem Dienst</em> passt.</h1>
      <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Unter-Text Hero -->
      <p class="hero-sub">Als Beamter hast du besondere Rechte und besonderen Versicherungsbedarf. Wir beraten dich unabhängig, individuell und komplett kostenlos – damit du den optimalen Schutz bekommst.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#berater" class="btn-primary">Jetzt kostenlos beraten lassen</a>
        <a href="#leistungen" class="btn-outline">Unsere Leistungen</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 1 Zahl -->
          <div class="stat-num">2.400<span class="stat-accent">+</span></div>
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 1 Label -->
          <div class="stat-label">Beamte erfolgreich beraten</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 2 Zahl -->
          <div class="stat-num">15<span class="stat-accent"> J.</span></div>
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 2 Label -->
          <div class="stat-label">Erfahrung im öffentlichen Dienst</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 3 Zahl -->
          <div class="stat-num">4,9<span class="stat-accent">★</span></div>
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 3 Label -->
          <div class="stat-label">Bewertung unserer Kunden</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 4 Zahl -->
          <div class="stat-num">100<span class="stat-accent">%</span></div>
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Statistik 4 Label -->
          <div class="stat-label">Unabhängige Beratung</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST BAR -->
<div class="trustbar">
  <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-dot"></div>Bundes- &amp; Landesbeamte</div>
  <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-dot"></div>Lehrende &amp; Richter</div>
  <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-dot"></div>Polizei &amp; Feuerwehr</div>
  <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-dot"></div>Kommunalbeamte</div>
  <div class="trust-item"><div class="trust-dot"></div>Anwärter &amp; Pensionäre</div>
</div>

<!-- LEISTUNGEN -->
<section class="section-tinted" id="leistungen">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow-text">Unsere Leistungen</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Individuell. Unabhängig. <em>Immer kostenlos.</em></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Wir nehmen uns Zeit für deine persönliche Situation. Keine Pauschallösungen, kein Verkaufsdruck – und das alles ohne einen Cent Kosten für dich.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="leistungen-grid">
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">01</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 1 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Beihilfe &amp; Private Krankenversicherung</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 1 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Als Beamter hast du Anspruch auf Beihilfe. Wir analysieren deine individuelle Situation und finden die optimale PKV-Ergänzung – kostenlos und ohne Verpflichtung.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">02</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 2 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Dienstunfähigkeitsabsicherung</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 2 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Dienstunfähigkeit trifft Beamte anders als Angestellte. Wir prüfen deine persönliche Versorgungslücke und finden gemeinsam die passende Absicherung.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">03</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 3 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Versorgungslücken &amp; Altersvorsorge</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 3 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Auch mit Pension gibt es Versorgungslücken. Wir analysieren deine persönliche Situation und zeigen dir, wie du optimal für das Alter abgesichert bist.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">04</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 4 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Haftpflicht &amp; Rechtsschutz</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 4 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Im Dienst gibt es besondere Haftungsrisiken. Wir schauen uns deine Situation genau an und empfehlen nur, was du wirklich brauchst.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">05</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 5 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Pflegeversicherung</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 5 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Die gesetzliche Pflegeversicherung deckt oft nicht genug. Wir prüfen individuell, welche Ergänzung wirklich zu dir passt – ohne Kostendruck.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="leistung-card">
        <span class="leistung-num">06</span>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 6 Titel -->
        <div class="leistung-title">Beratung für Anwärter</div>
        <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Leistung 6 Text -->
        <p class="leistung-text">Gerade verbeamtet? Jetzt die richtigen Weichen stellen. Wir begleiten dich individuell vom ersten Tag an – vollständig kostenlos für dich.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BERATER -->
<section class="section-light" id="berater">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow-text">Unser Team</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Deine <em>persönlichen Berater</em></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Kein Callcenter, kein Zufall. Du wählst direkt, mit wem du sprechen möchtest – alle gleich kompetent, alle für dich da.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="berater-grid">

      <div class="berater-card">
        <div class="berater-top">
          <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Berater 1 Avatar-Initialen -->
          <div class="berater-avatar">VE</div>
          <div>
            <!-- ✏️ BEARBEITEN: Berater 1 Name -->
